\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k+kt}{int}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{load\PYGZus{}smem\PYGZus{}b\PYGZus{}n}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{tid}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{\PYGZpc{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+m+mi}{32}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{c+c1}{// col 0\PYGZti{}31 由 32 线程加载; vec 版: b\PYGZus{}n = (tid \PYGZpc{} 32) * 4, t 0\PYGZti{}31, col 0\PYGZti{}127, 每个线程加载 4 个元素，32x4 = 128}
