\PYG{c+c1}{//   \PYGZhy{} RoPE 数学公式: 对每对相邻维度做 2D 旋转}
\PYG{c+c1}{//     [x1\PYGZsq{}]   [cos(θ)  \PYGZhy{}sin(θ)] [x1]}
